text: Dimče Gastarski (born April 24, 1975) is a Macedonian former professional basketball player who played for many clubs in Macedonia like MZT Skopje, Vardar and Karpoš Sokoli.http://basketball.eurobasket.com/player/Dimce_Gastarski/FYR- Macedonia/Vardar_Apave_Skopje/8348http://www.fiba.com/pages/eng/fa/player/p/pid/17505/sid/1398/tid/2604/tid2//_/1996_European_Championship_for_Men_22_and_Under_Qualifying_Round/index.html He is the older brother of Vlado Ilievski who is also basketball player. ==External links== * * ==References== Category:1975 births Category:Living people Category:KK MZT Skopje players Category:Macedonian men's basketball players Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Small forwards Category:Shooting guards
